hadiths[66]{hadithnumber,text}:
6982,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi ki shuruaat soney ki haalat mein sachey khuwab ke zariey hui. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo khuwab bhi dekhtey to wo subah ki roshni ki tarah samney aa jata aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghare-hira mein chaley jatey aur is mein tanha Allah ki yad kartey they chand muqarrara dinon ke liye ( yahan aatey (aur un dinon ka khane-pine ka saman bhi sath laatey. phir Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas wapas tashrif ley jatey aur wo phir itna hi khane-pine ka saman aap ke sath kar detiin yahan tak ke haq aap ke paas achcha aa gaya aur aap ghare-hira hi mein they. chunanche usmein farishta aap ke paas aaya aur kaha ke padhiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke main padha hua nahi hun. aakhir usne mujhey pakad liya aur zor se daaba aur khub daaba jiski wjah se mujh ko bahut takleef hui. phir usne mujhey chhod diya aur kaha ke padhiye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir wahi jawab diya ke main padha hua nahi hun. usne mujhey aisa daaba ke main be qaabu ho gaya ya unhon-ne apna zor khatm kar diya aur phir chhod kar us ne mujh se kaha ke padhiye apne rab ke naam se jisne paida kya hai. alfaz ( ما لم يعلم‏ ( tak. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaey to aap ke moondhon ke gosht ( dar ke maarey ( phadak rahe they. jab ghar mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dakhil huey to farmaya ke mujhey chadar udha do, mujhey chadar udha do, chunanche aapko chadar udha di gaee aur jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khof door ho gaya to farmaya ke Khadija mera haal kya ho gaya hai? phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna Sara haal bayan kya aur farmaya ke mujhey apni jaan ka dar hai. lekin Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha Allah ki qism aisa hargiz nahi ho sakta , aap khush rahiye Allah Taala aapko kabhi ruswa nahi karega . aap to sila rehmii kartey hain, baat sachchii boltey hain, naadaaron ka bojh uthatey hain, mehman nawazi kartey hain aur haq ki wjah se pesh aaney wali museebaton par logon ki madad kartey hain. phir aapko Khadija (Raziallahu anha) Warqa- bin Nofal bin Asad bin abdul-Uzzaa bin Qusaii ke paas laaiin jo Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke walid khuwelid ke bhai ke betey they. jo zamana jahiliyat mein Esai ho gaey they aur arabii likh letey they aur wo jitna Allah Taala chahta arabii mein Injeel ka tarjama likha kartey they, wo us waqt bahut boodhey ho gaey they aur beenaaii bhi jati rahi thi. unse Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : bhai ! apne bhatijey ki baat suno . Warqa- ne puchha : bhatijey tum kya dekhtey ho? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo dekha tha wo sunaya to Warqa ne kaha ke ye to wahi farishta ( Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ( hai jo Musa (Alaihissalam) par aaya tha. kash! main us waqt jawan hota jab tumhen tumhari qaum nikal degi aur zinda rahtaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya ye mujhey nikaaleingey ? Warqa ne kaha ke haan. jab bhi koi Nabi w rasool wo paigham lekar aaya jisey lekar aap aaey hain to iske sath dushmanii ki gaee aur agar maine tumharey wo din pa liye to main tumhari bharpur madad karunga lekin kuchh hi dinon baad Warqa ka intiqal ho gaya aur wahi ka silsile kat gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski wjah se itna gham tha ke aap ne kai martaba pahaad ki buland choti se apne aapko gira dena chaha lekin jab bhi aap kisi pahaad ki choti par chadhey taake is par se apne aapko gira dein to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aap ke samney aagey aur kaha ke ya Muhammad ! aap yaqinan Allah ke rasool hain. us se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko sukoon hota aur aap wapas aa jatey lekin jab wahi zyada dinon tak ruki rahi to aap ne aik martaba aur aisa irada kya lekin jab pahaad ki choti par chadhey to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) samney aaey aur isi tarah ki baat phir kahi . Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ( sura Al-Anaam ( mein lafz ( ‏‏‏‏فالق الإصباح‏ ( se murad din mein suraj ki roshni aur raat mein chaand ki roshni hai."
6983,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi nek aadmi ka achchha khuwab nabwooat ka chhiyaaleeswaan hissey hai.''
6984,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(achchhey) khuwab Allah ki taraf se hotey hain aur burey khuwab shaitan ki taraf se hotey hain.''
6985,unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke jab tum mein se koi aisa khuwab dekhey jisey wo pasand karta ho to wo Allah ki taraf se hota hai. is par Allah ki hamd karey aur usey bata dena chahiye lekin agar koi iske siwa koi aisa khuwab dekhta hai jo usey na-pasand hai to ye shaitan ki taraf se hota hai to iske shar se panah maangey aur kisi se aisey khuwab ka zikr na karey ye khuwab usey kuchh nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega.''
6986,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' achchha khuwab Allah ki taraf se hota hai aur bura khuwab shaitan ki taraf se, isliye agar koi bura khuwab dekhey to usey us se Allah ki panah maangnii chahiye aur baain taraf thookna chahiye ye khuwab usey koi nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega ''aur Abdullah-bin Yahya se unke walid ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Ubai Qatada ne bayan kya aur unse unke walid ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah bayan kya."
6987,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''momin ka khuwab nabwooat ke chhiyaalees hisson mein se aik hissa hota hai.''
6988,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''momin ka khuwab nabwooat ke chhiyaalees hisson mein se aik hissa hota hai.'' uski riwayat saabit, Humaid, Ishaq bin-Abdullah aur Shuaib ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ki unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
6989,unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna ke nek khuwab nabwooat ke chhiyaalees hisson mein se aik hissey hai.
6990,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nabwooat mein se sirf ab mubashshiraat baqi reh gaee hain. sahaba ne puchha ke mubashshiraat kya hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchhey khuwab ."
6991,kuchh logon ko khuwab mein shabe-qadr ( Ramazan ki) saat (7) aakhiri taareekhon mein dikhai gaee aur kuchh logon ko dikhai gaee ke wo aakhiri das taareekhon mein hogi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey aakhiri saat (7) taareekhon mein talash karo.
6992,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar main itney dinon qaid mein rehta jitney dinon Yusuf (Alaihissalam) padey rahe aur phir mere paas qaasid bulaney aata to main uski dawat qabool kar letaa.''
6993,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne mujhey khuwab mein dekha to kisi din mujhey bedaarii mein bhi dekhega aur shaitan meri sura mein nahi aa sakta. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Ibne-Sirin ne bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko koi shakhs aap ki sura mein dekhey."
6994,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne mujhey khuwab mein dekha to usne waqei dekha kyonke shaitan meri sura mein nahi aa sakta aur momin ka khuwab nabwooat ke chhiyaalees hisson mein se aik hissa hota hai.''
6995,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' achchhey khuwab Allah ki taraf se hotey hain aur burey khuwab shaitan ki taraf se to jo shakhs koi bura khuwab dekhey to apne baain taraf karwat lekar teen martaba thoo thoo karey aur shaitan se Allah ki panah maangey wo usko nuqsan nahi dega aur shaitan kabhi meri shakl mein nahi aa sakta. ''
6996,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne mujhey dekha us ne haq dekhaa.'' us riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Yunus ne aur Zohri ke bhatijey ne ki.
6997,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna ke jisne mujhey dekha us ne haq dekha kyonke shaitan mujh jaisa nahi bin sakta.
6998,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mujhey (mafaatiihul-kalim) diye gaey hain aur raub ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai aur pichhli raat mein soyaa hua tha ke zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan mere paas laaiin gain aur mere samney unhein rakh diya gayaa.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to is duniya se tashrif le gaey aur tum un khazaanon ki kunjiyon ko ulat palat kar rahe ho ya nikal rahe ho ya lot rahe ho.
6999,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''raat mujhey Kaba ke paas (khuwaab mein) dikhaya gaya. maine aik gehunwey rang ke aadmi ko dekha wo gehunwey rang ke kisi sabse khoobsurat aadmi ki tarah they, unke lambey khoobsurat baal they un sabse khoobsurat baalon ki tarah jo tum dekh sakey hogey. unmein unhon-ne kangha kya hua tha aur pani unse tapak raha tha aur wo 2 aadmiyon ke sahaarey ya (ye farmaya ke) 2 aadmiyon ke shaanon ke sahaarey Baitullah ka tawaaf kar rahe they. maine puchha ke ye kon sahib hain. mujhey bataya gaya ke ye Masih ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) hain. phir achcha maine aik ghunghriyaaley baal waley aadmi ko dekha jiski aik aankh kaani thi aur angoor ke daney ki tarah uthi hui thi, maine puchha ye kon hai? mujhey bataya gaya ke ye Masih dajjal hai."
7000,"aik sahib Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur kaha ke maine raat ko khuwab dekha hai aur unhon-ne waqia bayan kya aur is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Sulaiman-bin Kasir , Zohri ke bhatijey aur Sufiyan bin Husain ne Zohri se ki, unse Ubaidullah ne bayan kya aur unse Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya, aur Zubaidi ne Zohri se bayan kya, unse Ubaidullah ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Shuaib aur Ishaq bin Yahya ne Zohri se bayan kya ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kartey they, aur Mamar ne usey muttasilan nahi bayan kya lekin baad mein muttasilan bayan karne lagey they."
7001,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umme-Haraam binte-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif ley jaya kartey they, wo Ubada-bin-Samit ke nikah mein thin. aik din aap unke yahan gaey to unhon-ne aap ke samney khaney ki cheez pesh ki aur aap ka sar jhadney lagiin. us arse mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey phir bedaar huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa rahe they."
7002,"maine is par puchha : ya Rasulullah! aap kyon hans rahe hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney Allah ke rastey mein jang kartey huey pesh kiye gaey, us dariya ki pusht par, wo is tarah sawar hain jaisey badshah takht par hotey hain. Ishaq ko shak tha (hadees ke alfaz (ملوكا على الأسرة) they ya (ملوكا على الأسرة ke jaisey) unhon-ne kaha ke maine is par arz kya : ya Rasulullah! dua kijiye ke Allah mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye dua ki phir aap ne sar Mubarak rakha (aur so gaey) phir bedaar huey to muskuraa rahe they. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap kyon hans rahe hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney Allah ke rastey mein jang kartey pesh kiye gaey. jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pehli martaba farmaya tha. bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah se dua karein ke mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum sabse pahley logon mein hogi. chunanche umme-Haraam (rz), Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane mein samandari safar par gain aur jab samandar se bahar aaiin to sawari se gir kar Shahid ho gaiin."
7003,"unhon-ne muhajireen ke sath silsilae-ukhuwat qaaim karne ke liye Qura andazi ki to hamara Qura Usmaan-bin-Maz'oon (Raziallahu anhu) ke naam niklaa. phir ham ne unhein apne ghar mein thahraayaa. iske baad unhein aik bimari ho gaee jis mein unki wafat ho gaee. jab unki wafat ho gaee to unhein ghusl diya gaya aur unke kapdon ka kafan diya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. maine kaha Abu-Saaib (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) tum par Allah ki rehmat ho, tumharey mutaalliq meri gawahi hai ke tumhen Allah ne izzat bakhshii hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke tumhen kaisey malum hua ke Allah ne unhein izzat bakhshii hai. maine arz kya, mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon ya Rasulullah! phir Allah kisey izzat bakhshnega? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jahan tak unka talluq hai to yaqeeni cheez (maut) un par aa chuki hai aur Allah ki qism main bhi unke liye bhalai ki ummeed rakhta hun aur Allah ki qism main Rasulullah honey ke bawajud hutamii taur par nahi janta ke mere sath kya kya jaeyga unhon-ne iske baad kaha ke Allah ki qism iske baad main kabhi kisi ki Bara't (Tauba) nahi karoongii."
7004,iska mujhey ranj hua. (ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq koi baat yaqin ke sath malum nahi hai) chunanche main so gaee aur maine khuwab mein dekha ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye aik jari chashma hai. maine uski itlaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye unka nek amal hai.
7005,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchhey khuwab Allah ki taraf se hotey hain aur burey shaitan ki taraf se to tum mein jo koi bura khuwab dekhey jo usey na-pasand ho to usko chahiye ke apni baain taraf thookey aur us se Allah ki panah maangey wo usey hargiz nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega.
7006,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main soyaa hua tha ke mere paas doodh ka aik piyala laya gaya aur maine iska doodh piyaa. yahan tak ke uski sairaabii ka asar maine apne nakhunon mein zahir hota dekha, iske baad maine iska bacha hua de diya. aap ka ishara umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf tha sahaba ne puchha : aap ne uski tabeer kya ki ya rasoolullaah? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ilm ."
7007,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, main soyaa hua tha ke mere paas doodh ka aik piyala laya gaya aur maine usmein se piyaa , yahan tak ke maine sairaabii ka asar apne aas-paas mein numaayaan dekha. phir maine iska bacha hua umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko diya jo sahaba wahan maujood they, unhon-ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah! aap ne uski tabeer kya ki? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ilm murad hai."
7008,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine dekha ke log mere samney pesh kiye ja rahe hain wo qamees pahney huey hain. unmein kuchh ki qamees to sirf seeney tak ki hai aur kuchh ki us se badi hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey to unki qamees zameen se ghisat rahi thi. sahaba ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne uski kya tabeer ki? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Deen .
7009,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main soyaa hua tha ke maine logon ko apne samney pesh hotey dekha. wo qamees pahney huey they, unmein kuchh ki qamees to seeney tak ki thi aur kuchh ki us se badi thi aur mere samney umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) pesh kiye gaey to unki qamees (zameen se) ghisat rahi thi. sahaba ne puchha : ya Rasulullah! aap ne uski tabeer kya ki? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Deen uski tabeer hai."
7010,"mein aik halqe mein betha tha jis mein Sad bin Malik aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey they. wahan se Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) guzrey to logon ne kaha ke ye ahle-jannat mein se hain. maine unse kaha ke wo is tarah ki baat keh rahe hain. aap ne farmaya, Subhan-Allah unke liye munasib nahi ke wo aisi baat kahein jiska unhein ilm nahi hai. maine khuwab mein dekha tha ke aik sutoon aik harey-bharey baagh mein nasab kya hua hai us sutoon ke uper ke sirey par aik halqa ( عروة ( laga hua tha aur nichey ( munsif ( tha. ( munsif ( se murad khaadim hai phir kaha gaya ke is par chadh jao main chadh gaya aur maine halqa pakad liya, phir maine iska tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah ka jab intiqal ho gaya to wo ( العروة الوثقى ( ko pakdey huey hongey."
7011,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mujhey tum khuwab mein 2 martaba dikhai gaiin. aik shakhs tumhen resham ke aik tukdey mein uthaey liye ja raha tha, us ne mujh se kaha ke ye aap ki biwi hain, unke ( chehrey se) parda hataao. maine parda uthaya ke wo tumhen thin. maine sochaa ke agar ye khuwab Allah ki taraf se hai to wo khud hi anjam tak pahunchaaeyga.''"
7012,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum se shadi karne se pahley mujhey tum 2 martaba dikhai gain, maine dekha ke aik farishta tumhen resham ke aik tukdey mein uthaey huey hai. maine us se kaha ke kholo us ne khola to wo tum thin. maine kaha ke agar ye Allah ke paas se hai to wo khud hi usey anjam tak pahunchaaeyga. phir maine tumhen dekha ke farishta tumhen resham ke aik tukdey mein uthaey huey hai. maine kaha ke kholo! us ne khola to usmein tum thin, phir maine kaha ke ye to Allah ki taraf se hai jo zaroor pura hoga.''"
7013,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main (jawaameul-kalim) ke sath Nabi banaakr bheja gaya hun aur meri madad raub ke zariey ki gaee hai aur main soyaa hua tha ke zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan mere paas laai gain aur mere hath mein unhein rakh diya gaya aur Muhammad ne bayan kya ke mujh tak ye baat pahunchi hai ke (jawaameul-kalim) se murad ye hai ke bahut se mamley jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se pahley kitaabon mein likhe huey they, unko Allah Taala ne aik ya 2 maamlon ya usi jaisey mein jama kar diya hai."
7014,"maine ( khuwab ( dekha ke maano mein aik baagh mein hun aur baagh ke beech mein aik sutoon hai jiske uper ke sirey par aik halqa hai. kaha gaya ke is par chadh jao. maine kaha ke main iski taqat nahi rakhta. phir mere paas khaadim aaya aur us ne mere kapdey chadhaa diye phir main uper chadh gaya aur maine halqa pakad liya, abhi main usey pakdey hi huey tha ke aankh khul gaee. phir maine iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo baagh Islam ka baagh tha aur wo sutoon Islam ka sutoon tha aur wo halqa ( عروة الوثقى ( tha, tum hamesha Islam par mazbootii se jamey rahogey yahan tak ke tumhari wafat ho jaeygi."
7015,maine khuwab mein dekha ke maano mere hath mein resham ka aik tukda hai aur main jannat mein jis jagah jana chahta hun wo mujhey uda kar wahan pahuncha deta hai. maine iska zikr Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kya.
7016,aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us khuwab ka zikr kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhara bhai mard nek ya farmaya ke Abdullah nek aadmi hai.
7017,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab qiyamat qareeb hogi to momin ka khuwab jhoota nahi hoga aur momin ka khuwab nabwooat ke chhiyaalees hisson mein se aik hissey hai.'' Muhammad-bin Sirin (Rahmatullahi-alaih) (jo ke ilme-ta'beer ke bahut badey aalim they) ne kaha ke nabwooat ka hissa jhoot nahi ho sakta. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke khuwab teen tarah ke hain. dil ke khayaalaat, shaitan ka daraanaa aur Allah ki taraf se khushkhabrii. to agar koi shakhs khuwab mein buri cheez dekhta hai to usey chahiye ke uska zikr kisi se na karey aur khada ho kar Namaz padhney lagey Muhammad-bin-Siiriin ne kaha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) khuwab mein tauq ko na-pasand kartey they aur qaid dekhney ko achchha samajhtey they aur kaha gaya hai ke qaid se murad Deen mein Sabit qadmii hai. aur Qataada, Younus, Hisham aur abu-Hilaal ne Ibne-Sirin se naql kya hai, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. aur kuchh ne ye saari riwayat hadis mein shumaar ki hai lekin Auf ki riwayat zyada waazeh hai aur Yunus ne kaha ke qaid ke barey mein riwayat ko main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis hi samajhta hun. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke tauq hamesha gardanon hi mein hotey hain."
7018,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi. unhon-ne bayan kya ke jab Ansar ne muhajireen ke qiyam ke liye Qura andazi ki to Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam hamarey yahan thaharney ke liye niklaa. phir wo bimar pad gaey, ham ne unki teemaardaarii ki lekin unki wafat ho gaee. phir ham ne unhein unke kapdon mein lapet diya. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey ghar tashrif laey to maine kaha : Abu-Saaib ! tum par Allah ki rahmatein hon, meri gawahi hai ke tumhen Allah Taala ne izzat bakhshii hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen ye kaisey malum hua? maine arz kya : Allah ki qism mujhey malum nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad farmaya ke jahan tak unka talluq hai to yaqeeni baat (maut) un tak pahunch chuki hai aur main Allah se unke liye khair ki ummeed rakhta hun lekin Allah ki qism main Rasulullah hun aur uske bawajud mujhey malum nahi ke mere sath kya mamla kya jaeyga ummul-Ulaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qasam! iske baad main kisi insan ki paakii nahi bayan karoongii. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye khuwab mein aik jari chashma dekha tha. chunanche maine hazir ho kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye unka nek amal hai jiska sawab unke liye jari hai."
7019,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ( khuwab mein) mein aik kuwein se pani kheench raha tha ke Abu-Bakar aur umr bhi aa gaey. ab Abu-Bakar ne dol ley liya aur aik ya 2 dol pani kheenchaa . unke kheenchney mein kamzori thi. Allah Taala unki maghfirat karey Aameen . iske baad umr bin-Khattab ne usey Abu-Bakar ke hath se ley liya aur wo dol unke hath mein bada dol bin gaya. maine umr jaisa pani kheenchney mein kisi ko maahir nahi dekha. unhon-ne khub pani nikala yahan tak ke logon ne oonton ke liye pani se hauz bhar liye.''
7020,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke khuwab ke silsiley mein farmaya ke maine logon ko dekha ke jama ho gaey hain phir Abu-Bakar khadey huey aur aik ya 2 dol pani kheenchaa aur unke kheenchney mein kamzori thi, Allah unki maghfirat kare. phir umr bin-Khattab khadey huey aur wo bada dol bin gaya. maine logon mein se kisi ko itni maharat ke sath pani nikaaltey nahi dekha yahan tak ke logon ne hauz bhar liye."
7021,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine apne aapko aik kuwein par dekha. is par aik dol tha. jitna Allah ne chaha maine usmein se pani kheenchaa, phir us dol ko ibne-abii-qahaafa ne ley liya aur unhon-ne bhi aik ya 2 dol kheenchney aur unke kheenchney mein kamzori thi, Allah unki maghfirat karey phir wo bada dol bin gaya aur usey umr bin-Khattab ne utha liya. maine kisi maahir ko umr bin-Khattab ki tarah kheenchtey nahi dekha yahan tak ke unhon-ne logon ke liye oonton ke hauz bhar diye. logon ne apne oonton ko sairaab karke apne thaanon par ley ja kar betha diyaa.''"
7022,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine khuwab dekha ke main hauz par hun aur logon ko sairaab kar raha hun phir mere paas Abu-Bakar aaey aur mujhey aaraam dene ke liye dol mere hath se ley liya phir unhon-ne 2 dol kheenchey unke kheenchney mein kamzori thi, Allah unki maghfirat kare. phir umr bin-Khattab aaey aur unse dol ley liya aur barabar kheenchey rahe yahan tak ke log sairaab ho kar chal diye aur hauz se pani labaalab ubal raha tha.''"
7023,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine apne aapko jannat mein dekha. maine dekha ke jannat ke mahal ke aik kinarey aik aurat wuzu kar rahi hai. maine puchha : ye mahal kis ka hai? bataya ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kaa. phir maine unki ghairat yad ki aur wahan se lot gayaa.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) is par ro padey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon, kya main aap par ghairat karoonga?"
7024,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main jannat mein dakhil hua to wahan aik soney ka mahal mujhey nazar aaya. maine puchha ye kis ka hai? kaha ke Quraish ke aik shakhs kaa. aey ibne-Khattaab! mujhey iske andar janey se tumhari ghairat ne rok diya hai jisey main khub janta hoon.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya main aap par ghairat karunga .
7025,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine apne aapko jannat mein dekha wahan aik aurat aik mahal ke kinarey wuzu kar rahi thi. maine puchha ye mahal kis ka hai? kaha umr (Raziallahu anhu) kaa. phir maine unki ghairat yad ki aur wahan se lot kar chala aaya. ''is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ro diye aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon, kya aap par ghairat karunga ."
7026,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine apne aapko Kaba ka tawaaf kartey dekha. achcha aik sahib nazar aaey, gehunwey rang ke baal latkey huey they aur 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan ( sahara liye huey they) unke sar se pani tapak raha tha. maine puchha ye kon hain? kaha ke Esa ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) , phir main mudaa to aik doosra shakhs surkh , bhari jism waalaa, ghungariyaaley baal wala aur aik aankh se kaana jaisey uski aankh par khushk angoor ho nazar aaya. maine puchha ye kon hain? kaha ke ye dajjal hai. uski sura abdul-Uzzaa-bin-qatan se bahut miltii thii.'' ye abdul-Uzzaa bin qatan mustaliq mein se tha jo qabila khuza'aa ki aik shaakh hai."
7027,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ke main soyaa hua tha ke doodh ka aik piyala mere paas laya gaya aur is mein se itna piyaa ke sairaabii ko maine har rag w pay mein paya. phir maine apna bacha hua doodh umr ko de diya. logon ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool! aap ne uski tabeer kya ki? farmaya ke ilm uski tabeer hai."
7028,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se kuchh log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein khuwab dekhtey they aur usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kartey they, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski tabeer detey jaisa ke Allah chaahtaa. main us waqt naujawaan tha aur mera ghar masjid thi ye meri shadi se pahley ki baat hai. maine apne dil mein sochaa ke agar tujh mein koi khair hoti to too bhi un logon ki tarah khuwab dekhta . chunanche jab main aik raat leta to maine kaha : aey Allah ! agar to mere andar koi khair w bhalai janta hai to mujhey koi khuwab dikhaa . main usi haal main ( so gaya aur maine dekha ke) mere paas 2 Farishtey aaey, unmein se har aik ke hath mein lohey ka hathodaa tha aur wo mujhey jahannam ki taraf ley chaley. mein un donon farishton ke darmyan mein tha aur Allah se dua karta ja raha tha ke aey Allah ! main jahannam se teri panah mangta hun phir mujhey dikhaya gaya ( khuwab hi mein) ke mujh se aik aur farishta mila jiske hath mein lohey ka aik hathodaa tha aur us ne kaha daro nahi tum kitney achchhey aadmi ho agar tum Namaz zyada padhtey . chunanche wo mujhey lekar chaley aur jahannam ke kinarey par ley ja kar mujhey khada kar diya to jahannam aik gol kuwein ki tarah thi aur kuwein ke matkon ki tarah uske bhi matkey they aur har 2 matkon ke darmyan aik farishta tha. jiske hath mein lohey ka aik hathodaa tha aur maine usmein kuchh log dekhey jinhein zanjeeron mein latkaa diya gaya tha aur unke sar nichey they. (aur paon uper ( unmein se kuchh Quraish ke logon ko maine pehchaana bhi, phir wo mujhey daain taraf lekar chaley."
7029,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye ( sun kar) farmaya, Abdullah mard nek hai, (agar raat ko tahajjud padhta hota ( Naafe kehtey hain ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab se ye khuwab dekha wo nafl Namaz bahut padha kartey they. matkey jin par mooth ki lakdiyan khadi kartey hain."
7030,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein naujawaan ghair shadi shuda tha to masjide-Nabawi mein sota tha aur jo shakhs bhi khuwab dekhta wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uska tazkira karta. maine sochaa : aey Allah ! agar terey nazdeek mujh mein koi khair hai to mujhey bhi koi khuwab dikhaa jiski Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey tabeer dein. phir main soyaa aur maine 2 Farishtey dekhey jo mere paas aaey aur mujhey ley chaley. phir un donon se tesraa farishta bhi aa mila aur us ne mujh se kaha ke daro nahi tum nek aadmi ho. phir wo donon Farishtey mujhey jahannam ki taraf le gaey to wo kuwein ki tarah teh-b-teh thi aur is mein kuchh log they jin mein se kuchh ko maine pehchaana bhi, phir wo donon Farishtey mujhey daain taraf ley chaley, jab subah hui to maine us tazkira apni behan Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kya."
7031,Ummul-Momenin Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us khuwab ka zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah nek mard hai. kash! wo raat mein Namaz zyada padha karta. Zohri ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us farman ke baad wo raat mein nafli Namaz zyada padha kartey they.
7032,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main soyaa hua tha ke mere paas doodh ka piyala laya gaya. maine usmein se piyaa phir maine apna bacha hua umr bin-Khattab ko de diya. logon ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne uski tabeer kya li ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ilm se tabeer li."
7033,maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us khuwab ke mutaalliq puchha jo unhon-ne bayan kya tha.
7034,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine khuwab mein dekha ke 2 soney ke kangan mere hath mein rakhey gaey hain to mujhey us se takleef pahunchi aur na-gawar hui phir mujhey ijazat di gaee aur maine un par phoonk maari aur wo donon ud gaey. maine uski tabeer li ke 2 jhootey paida hongey. Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke unmein se aik to Ansii tha jisey Yaman mein feeroz ne qatl kya aur doosra Musailma.
7035,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya maine khuwab dekha ke main Makka se aik aisi zameen ki taraf hijrat kar raha hun jahan khajoorein hain. mera zahan us taraf gaya ke ye jagah yamaama hai ya hijr . lekin baad mein malum hua ke Madina yani yasrib hai aur maine khuwab mein gaaey dekhi (zabah ki hui) aur ye awaz suni ke koi keh raha hai ke aur Allah ke yahan hi khair hai to uski tabeer un musalmanon ki sura mein aai jo jange-Uhud mein Shahid huey aur khair wo hai jo Allah Taala ne khair aur sachchai ke sawab ki sura mein diya yani wo jo hamein Allah Taala ne jange-badr ke baad (doosri futoohaat ki sura mein) di.
7036,ye wo hadis hai jo ham se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ham sab ummaton se aakhiri ummat (waqt ke eitibaar se) aur sab ummaton se pehli ummat (jannat mein daakhila ke eitibaar se) hain.''
7037,aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke zameen ke khazaaney mere paas laey gaey aur mere hath mein 2 soney ke kangan rakh diye gaey jo mujhey bahut sakht guzrey . phir mujhey wahi ki gaee ke main un par phoonk maarun maine phoonkaa to wo ud gaey. maine unki tabeer 2 jhooton se li jinke darmyan mein main hun aik san'aa ka aur doosra yamaama kaa. ''
7038,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine dekha jaisey aik siyah aurat bikhrey huey baal, Madina se nikli aur Mahya' mein ja kar khadi ho gaee. Mahya' Johfa ko kehtey hain. maine uski ye tabeer li ke Madina ki wabaa Johfa naam ke basti mein chali gaee."
7039,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Madina mein khuwab ke silsiley mein ke (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya) ''maine aik bikhrey huey baal, siyah aurat dekhi ke wo Madina se nikal kar Mahya' chali gaee. maine uski tabeer li ke Madina ki wabaa Mahya muntaqil ho gaee hai.'' Mahya' yani Johfa ko kehtey hain."
7040,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maine aik bikhrey huey baal, kali aurat dekhi jo Madina se nikli aur Mahya' main ja kar thahar gaee. maine uski tabeer ye li ke Madina ki wabaa Mahya' yani muntaqil ho gaii.''"
7041,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya ke maine aik talwaar hilaaii to wo beech se toot gaee. uski tabeer Uhud ki jang mein musalmanon ke Shahid honey ki sura mein samney aai phir dobara maine usey hilaayaa to wo pahley se bhi achi shakl mein ho gaee. uski tabeer fateh aur musalmanon ke ittifaq w ijtimaa ki sura mein samney aai.
7042,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne aisa khuwab bayan kya jo usney dekha na ho to usey 2 jau ke 2 daanon ko qiyamat ke din jodney ke liye kaha jaeyga aur wo usey hargiz nahi kar sakega (is liye mar khata rahega (aur jo shakhs doosrey logon ki baat sunney ke liye kaan lagaey jo usey pasand nahi kartey ya us se bhaagtey hain to qiyamat ke din iske kanon mein seesa pighlaa kar daala jaeyga aur jo koi tasweer banaaeyga usey azab diya jaeyga aur is par zor diya jaeyga ke usmein Rooh bhi daley jo wo nahi kar sakega aur Sufiyan ne kaha ke ham se Ayub ne ye hadis mausoolan bayan ki aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne bayan kya, ham se abu-Awana ne, unse Qatada ne, unse Ikrima ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke jo apne khuwab ke silsiley mein jhoot boley aur Shoba ne kaha, unse abu-Haashim ramaanii ne, unhon-ne Ikrima se suna aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ka qaul mauqoofan) jo shakhs moorat banaaey, jo shakhs jhoota khuwab bayan karey, jo shakhs kaan laga kar dusron ki baatein suney. ham se Ishaq waastii ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Khalid Tahan ne bayan kya, unse Khalid hazaa ne, unse Ikrima ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jo kisi ki baat kaan laga kar sunney ke peechhey laga aur jisne ghalat khuwab bayan kya aur jisne tasweer banai (aisii hi hadis naql ki Mauqoofan Ibne-Abbas se) Khalid hazaa ke sath is hadis ko Hisham bin Hassan Firdausi ne bhi Ikrima se, unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se mauqoofan riwayat kya."
7043,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse badtareen jhoot ye hai ke insan khuwab mein aisi cheez ko dekhney ka dawa karey jo uski aankhon ne na dekhi ho.''
7044,"maine abu-Salma se suna, unhon-ne kaha ke main ( burey ( khuwab dekhta tha aur uski wjah se bimar pad jata tha. aakhir maine Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne bayan kya ke main bhi khuwab dekhta aur main bhi bimar pad jata. aakhir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna ke achchhey khuwab Allah ki taraf se hotey hain to jab koi achchhey khuwab dekhey to uska zikr sirf usi se karey jo usey azeez ho aur jab bura khuwab dekhey to Allah ki iske shar se panah maangey aur shaitan ke shar se aur teen martaba thoo-thoo kar de aur iska kisi se zikr na karey to wo usey hargiz koi nuqsan na pahuncha sakega."
7045,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi shakhs khuwab dekhey jisey wo pasand karta ho to wo Allah ki taraf se hota hai aur is par usey Allah ki tareef karna chahiye aur usey bayan bhi karna chahiye aur jab koi khuwab aisa dekhey jisey wo na-pasand karta ho to wo shaitan ki taraf se hai aur usey chahiye ke iske shar se Allah ki panah maangey aur iska zikr kisi se na karey, kyonke wo usey hargiz nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega."
7046,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur us ne kaha ke raat maine khuwab mein dekha ke aik abr ka tukda hai jis se ghi aur shehad tapak raha hai main dekhta hun ke log unhein apne hathon mein ley rahe hain. koi zyada aur koi kam aur aik rassii hai jo zameen se aasman tak latkii hui hai. maine dekha ke pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aa kar usey pakad aur uper chadh gaey phir aik doosrey sahib ne bhi usey pakda aur wo bhi uper chadh gaey phir aik teesrey sahib ne pakda aur wo bhi chadh gaey phir chauthey sahib ne pakda aur wo bhi iske zariey chadh gaey. phir wo rassii toot gaee, phir jad gaee Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon. mujhey ijazat dijiye main uski tabeer bayan kar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bayan karo. unhon-ne kaha saaye se murad deene-Islam hai aur shehad aur ghi tapak raha tha wo Quran Majeed ki mithas hai aur kuchh Quran ko zyada hasil karne waley hain, kuchh kam aur aasman se zameen tak ki rassii se murad wo sachcha tareeq hai jis par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qaaim hain, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey pakdey huey hain yahan tak ke iske zariey Allah aapko utha lega phir aap ke baad aik doosrey sahib aap ke khaleefa awwal usey pakdengey wo bhi martey dam tak is par qaaim rahengey . phir teesrey sahib pakdein gey unka bhi yahi haal hoga. phir chauthey sahib pakdengey to unka mamla khilafat ka kat jaeyga wo bhi uper chadh jaengey. ya Rasulullah! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hon mujhey bataiye kya maine jo tabeer di hai wo ghalat hai ya saheeh. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuchh hisse ki sahi tabeer di hai aur kuchh ki ghalat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : to Allah ki qism ! aap meri ghalati ko zahir farma dein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qism na khaao."
7047,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo baatein sahaba se aksar kya kartey they unmein ye bhi thi ke tum mein se kisi ne koi khuwab dekha hai. bayan kya ke phir jo chahta apna khuwab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan karta aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik subah ko farmaya ke raat mere paas 2 aaney waley aaey aur unhon-ne mujhey uthaya aur mujh se kaha ke hamarey sath chalo. main unke sath chal diya. phir ham aik letey huey shakhs ke paas aaey jiske paas aik doosra shakhs patthar liye khada tha aur uske sar par patthar phenk kar maarta to uska sar us se phat jata, patthar ludhak kar door chala jata, lekin wo shakhs patthar ke peechhey jata aur usey utha laataa aur us letey huey shakhs tak pahunchne se pahley hi iska sar theek ho jata jaisa ke pahley tha. khada shakhs phir isi tarah patthar is par maarta aur wahi sooratein pesh aatiin jo pahley pesh aai thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine un donon se puchha Subhan-Allah ye donon kon hain? farmaya ke mujh se unhon-ne kaha ke aagey badho , aagey badho . farmaya ke phir ham aagey badhey aur aik aisey shakhs ke paas pahunchey jo peeth ke bal leta hua tha aur aik doosra shakhs uske paas lohey ka aankda liye khada tha aur ye iske chehra ke aik taraf aata aur uske aik jabdey ko guddi tak cheertaa aur uski naak ko guddi tak cheertaa aur uski aankh ko guddi tak cheertaa. ( Auf ne) bayan kya ke kuchh baar abu-Rijaa ( rawi hadis) ne ( فيشق ( kaha, ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) bayan kya ke phir wo dusri taraf jata idhar bhi isi tarah cheertaa jis tarah us ne pehli taraf kya tha. wo abhi dusri taraf se farigh bhi na hota tha ke pehli taraf apni pehli sahi haalat mein lot aatii. phir dobara wo isi tarah karta jis tarah us ne pehli martaba kya tha. (is tarah barabar ho raha hai) farmaya ke maine kaha Subhan-Allah ! ye donon kon hai? unhon-ne kaha ke aagey chalo , ( abhi kuchh na poochho ( chunanche ham aagey chaley phir ham aik tannoor jaisi cheez par aaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke aap kaha kartey they ke usmein shor w awaz thi. kaha ke phir ham ne usmein jhanka to iske andar kuchh nangey mard aur auratein thin aur unke nichey se aag ki lapat aati thi jab aag unhein apni lapet mein leti to wo chalaney lagtey. (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya ke maine unse puchha ye kon log hain. unhon-ne kaha ke chalo aagey chalo. farmaya ke ham aagey badhey aur aik nehar par aaey. mera khayal hai ke aap ne kaha ke wo khoon ki tarah surkh thi aur us nehar mein aik shakhs tair raha tha aur nehar ke kinarey aik doosra shakhs tha jisne apne paas bahut se patthar jama kar rakhey they aur ye tairney wala tairtaa hua jab us shakhs ke paas pahunchtaa jisne patthar jama kar rakhey they, to ye apna munh khol deta aur kinarey ka shakhs uske munh mein patthar daal deta wo phir tairney lagta aur phir uske paas lot kar aata aur jab bhi uske paas aata to apna munh phaila deta aur ye iske munh mein patthar daal deta. farmaya ke maine puchha ye kon hain? farmaya ke unhon-ne kaha ke chalo aagey chalo. farmaya ke phir ham aagey badhey aur aik bahut hi zyada bad-soorat aadmi ke paas pahunchey jitney bad-soorat tum ne dekhey hongey unmein sabse zyada bad-soorat . uske paas aag jal rahi thi aur wo usey jalaa raha tha aur uske charon taraf daudta tha (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya ke maine unse kaha ke ye kya hai? farmaya ke unhon-ne mujh se kaha chalo aagey chalo. ham aagey badhey aur aik aisey baagh mein pahunchey jo haraa bharaa tha aur is mein mausam bahaar ke sab phool they. us baagh ke darmyan mein bahut lamba aik shakhs tha, itna lamba tha ke mere liye iska sar dekhnaa dushwar tha ke wo aasman se baatein karta tha aur us shakhs ke charon taraf se bahut se bachchey they ke itney kabhi nahi dekhey they (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya ke maine puchha ye kon hai ye bachchey kon hain? farmaya ke unhon-ne mujh se kaha ke chalo aagey chalo farmaya ke phir ham aagey badhey aur aik azimushshan baagh tak pahunchey, maine itna bada aur khoobsurat baagh kabhi nahi dekha tha. un donon ne kaha ke is par chadhiye ham is par chadhey to aik aisa Shahar dikhai diya jo is tarah bana tha ke uski aik iint soney ki thi aur aik iint chandi ki. ham Shahar ke darwazey par aaey to ham ne usey khulwaya . wo hamarey liye khola gaya aur ham usmein dakhil huey. ham ne usmein aisey logon se mulaqat ki jinke jism ka nisf hissey to bahut hi zyada khoobsurat tha aur doosra nisf bahut hi zyada bad-soorat . (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya ke donon sathiyon ne un logon se kaha ke jao aur us nehar mein kood jao . aik nehar samney bah rahi thi iska pani intihai safaid tha wo log gaey aur is mein kood gaey aur phir hamarey paas lot kar aaey to unka pahlaa aib ja chuka tha aur ab wo bahut hi zyada khoobsurat ho gaey they (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya ke un donon ne kaha ke ye jannat adn hai aur ye aap ki manzil hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) farmaya ke meri nazar uper ki taraf uthi to safaid badal ki tarah aik mahal uper nazar aaya farmaya ke unhon-ne mujh se kaha ke ye aap ki manzil hai. farmaya ke maine unse kaha Allah Taala tumhen barkat de. mujhey usmein dakhil honey do. unhon-ne kaha ke is waqt to aap nahi ja saktey lekin haan aap usmein zaroor jaengey. farmaya ke maine unse kaha ke aaj raat maine ajeeb w ghareeb cheezein dekhi hain. ye cheezein kya thin jo maine dekhi hain. farmaya ke unhon-ne mujh se kaha ham aapko bataaeingey. pahlaa shakhs jiske paas aap gaey they aur jiska sar patthar se kuchlaa ja raha tha ye wo shakhs hai jo Quran seekhtaa tha aur phir usey chhod deta aur farz Namaz ko chhod kar so jata aur wo shakhs jiske paas aap gaey aur jiska jabdaa guddi tak aur naak guddi tak aur aankh guddi tak cheerii ja rahi thi. ye wo shakhs hai jo subah apne ghar se nikalta aur jhooti khabar taraashtaa, jo duniya mein phail jati aur wo nangey mard aur auratein jo tannoor mein aap ne dekhey wo zina kaar mard aur auratein thin wo shakhs jiske paas aap us haal mein gaey ke wo nehar mein teer raha tha aur uske munh mein patthar diya jata tha wo sood khaney wala hai aur wo shakhs jo bad-soorat hai aur jahannam ki aag bhadkaa raha hai aur uske charon taraf chal phir raha hai wo jahannam ka darogha Malik naam ke hai aur wo lamba shakhs jo baagh mein nazar aaya wo Ibrahim hain aur jo bachchey unke charon taraf hain to wo bachchey hain jo (bachpan hi mein) fitrat par mar gaey hain. bayan kya ke is par kuchh musalmanon ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! kya mushrekeen ke bachchey bhi unmein dakhil hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, mushrekeen ke bachchey bhi (unmein dakhil hain) ab rahe wo log jinka aadha jism khoobsurat aur aadha bad-soorat tha to ye wo log they jinhoney achchhey amal ke sath burey amal bhi kiye Allah Taala ne unke gunahon ko bakhsh diya."
